foster family will also bring the dog to at least one of our off-site events every two months (or more if they want).  They can even leave the dog at the event and do some shopping or run errands!<a href=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/yoyo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-79\" title=\"yoyo\" src=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/yoyo-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>  Halfway Home means just that, the dog is “half way” to finding its forever home.  By doing this, the dog gets some time in a home with a family to be even more social.  We’ve already seen success with the program and we’re looking to expand.  Right now we have three dogs looking for Halfway Home fosters.  Macy, Edison and Yoyo are three great dogs who for whatever reason keep getting passed up by adopters.  If you can open your heart and your home to any of our amazing dogs be sure to check out our foster program today at <a title=\"www.adltexas.org\" href=\"http://adltexas.org/programs-services/foster-care/\">http://adltexas.org/programs-services/foster-care/</a>!'),(875,76,'save','Update'),(876,76,'wp-preview',''),(877,76,'hidden_post_status','publish'),(878,76,'post_status','publish'),(879,76,'hidden_post_password',''),(880,76,'hidden_post_visibility','public'),(881,76,'visibility','public'),(882,76,'post_password',''),(883,76,'mm','08'),(884,76,'jj','30'),(885,76,'aa','2012'),(886,76,'hh','17'),(887,76,'mn','19'),(888,76,'ss','24'),(889,76,'hidden_mm','08'),(890,76,'cur_mm','08'),(891,76,'hidden_jj','30'),(892,76,'cur_jj','31'),(893,76,'hidden_aa','2012'),(894,76,'cur_aa','2012'),(895,76,'hidden_hh','17'),(896,76,'cur_hh','08'),(897,76,'hidden_mn','19'),(898,76,'cur_mn','14'),(899,76,'original_publish','Update'),(900,76,'post_format','0'),(901,76,'post_category','a:2:{i:0;s:1:\"0\";i:1;s:2:\"12\";}'),(902,76,'newcategory','New Category Name'),(903,76,'newcategory_parent','-1'),(904,76,'_ajax_nonce-add-category'