lf in foster for nearly a year. After returning from foster in early December 2013, Sophie was placed up for adoption and waited patiently for her forever home. A few short weeks after being placed up for adoption, I am happy to announce that Sophie has found her forever home. She was adopted by a fantastic and loving family. Sophie is a great example of the benefits of fostering and is a true foster to adoption success story.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_217\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"273\"]<a href=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/sophie.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-216\" alt=\"Sophie A Few Days Before Adoption\" src=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/sophie-224x300.jpg\" width=\"224\" height=\"300\" /></a> Sophie Back From Foster[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_217\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"273\"]<a href=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Sophiie-Adoption.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-217\" alt=\"Sophie on her big day! \" src=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Sophiie-Adoption-273x300.jpg\" width=\"273\" height=\"300\" /></a> Sophie on her big day![/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor more information regarding the Foster Program, please contact 210.655.1481 ext.123 or by email at <a href=\"mailto:foster@adltexas.org\">foster@adltexas.org</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(2059,215,'wp-preview',''),(2060,215,'hidden_post_status','publish'),(2061,215,'post_status','publish'),(2062,215,'hidden_post_password',''),(2063,215,'hidden_post_visibility','public'),(2064,215,'visibility','public'),(2065,215,'post_password',''),(2066,215,'mm','01'),(2067,215,'jj','08'),(2068,215,'aa','2014'),(2069,215,'hh','10'),(2070,215,'mn','23'),(2071,215,'ss','03'),(2072,215,'hidden_mm','01'),(2073,215,'cur_mm','01'),(2074,215,'hidden_jj','08'),(2075,215,'cur_jj','08'),(2076,215,'hidden_aa','2014'),(2077,215,'cur_aa','2014'),(2078,215,'hidden_hh','10'),(2079,215,'cur_hh',