’ve already seen success with the program and we’re looking to expand.  Right now we have three dogs looking for Halfway Home fosters.  Macy, Edison and Yoyo are three great dogs who for whatever reason keep getting passed up by adopters.  If you can open your heart and your home to any of our amazing dogs be sure to check out our foster program today at <a title=\"www.adltexas.org\" href=\"http://adltexas.org/programs-services/foster-care/\">http://adltexas.org/programs-services/foster-care/</a>!','Halfway Home','','publish','open','open','','halfway-home','','http://adltexas.org/programs-services/foster-care/\nhttp://adltexas.org/programs-services/foster-care/','2012-08-31 08:15:12','2012-08-31 13:15:12','',0,'http://blog.adltexas.org/?p=76',0,'post','',0),(77,2,'2012-08-30 17:11:05','2012-08-30 22:11:05','','edisonpic','','inherit','open','open','','edisonpic','','','2012-08-30 17:11:05','2012-08-30 22:11:05','',76,'http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/edisonpic.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(78,2,'2012-08-30 17:11:07','2012-08-30 22:11:07','','macy','','inherit','open','open','','macy','','','2012-08-30 17:11:07','2012-08-30 22:11:07','',76,'http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/macy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(79,2,'2012-08-30 17:11:24','2012-08-30 22:11:24','','yoyo','','inherit','open','open','','yoyo','','','2012-08-30 17:11:24','2012-08-30 22:11:24','',76,'http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/yoyo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(80,2,'2012-08-30 17:15:30','2012-08-30 22:15:30','<a href=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/macy.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-78\" title=\"macy\" src=\"http://blog.adltexas.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/macy-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Here at the Animal Defense League, we are responsible for hundreds of cats and dogs.  Some of these animals are in our foster care program.  Usually, these are “bo